data.description: Nestled on corner lot privately in quiet cove, home enjoys 4BR/2.5BA. Inside find soaring ceilings, HW floors, & extensive crown molding. FP highlights family-sized great RM. It opens to the dining RM, ideal for holiday gatherings. Gourmet kitchen enjoys a large island w/bar seating, granite countertops, tons of cabinet space, soaring ceilings & an adjoining breakfast area. 1/2BA & laundry RM just off kitchen. Primary BR w/luxury suite down. 3BR/1BA Up. 2-car garage. Agent Owner.
